ComicInfo.Summary: XI: The Unnamable: Robert Black, done with his investigations into the occult, returns to New York as a mentally and spiritually broken man. H.P. Lovecraft's fiction, inspired by Black's experiences, becomes widely known, and its influence begins to cause occult events.
